# Customer Sales Analysis (SQL)

## Overview
This project focuses on analyzing customer sales data using SQL to generate insights on revenue, customer behavior, and product performance.

## Dataset Description
The dataset includes:
- Customer details  
- Product information  
- Sales transactions  

## Objectives
- Identify top customers based on total spending  
- Analyze sales performance by product category  
- Track monthly revenue trends  
- Understand customer purchase behavior  

## SQL Concepts Used
- SELECT, WHERE, ORDER BY  
- GROUP BY & Aggregate Functions  
- JOINS  
- Subqueries  
- Window Functions  

## Tools Used
SQL (MySQL/PostgreSQL)

## Outcome
- Identified top revenue-generating customers  
- Analyzed product category performance  
- Generated monthly sales trends  
- Improved understanding of customer purchasing patterns  
